---
title: Honey-Soy Beef Strips with Peanut Sauce & Jasmine Rice
description: Nutty, flavoursome and incredibly moreish, this stir-fry brings together quick-cooking beef strips with a colourful array of veggies. The creamy peanut sauce is the icing on top of this tasty family meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-soy-beef-stir-fry-73d95192.jpg
